{"tid":535330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企氣氛好冷淡","createTime":"2018-01-20T17:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T18:20:35.000Z","uid":136192,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d057112cdb3f10567de9ba8ccf191772a96cb0a9","tid":535330,"uid":136192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:20:22.000Z","msg":"老豆老母反晒面<br />\n雖然冇離婚但係一啲溫馨既感覺都冇 貌合神離<br />\n講句野都要搵我黎傳話<br />\n夾係中間好撚辛苦呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成屋一齊出去行街食飯圍埋傾計唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次番到屋企見到咁情況都好撚灰<br />\n屌 <br />\n好撚羨慕人地人地家庭咁溫暖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2b7a2292c3fd2559d8e0e39dfb43bbcdb72158","tid":535330,"uid":136192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"好撚灰呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到個屋企咁都無晒心機 唔想番屋企呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1517bd98b7e7800316788525c719d5fc806276de","tid":535330,"uid":5899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:26:43.000Z","msg":"同你情況差唔多 佢地係我小學個陣已經反哂面分房訓 各自出面都有第三者 之後十幾年黎嘈過打過警都報埋社工又搵過 自己識諗之後明白佢地已經冇可能返轉頭 所以乜都慣哂麻木哂"},{"pid":"97d30f0139279b52fe56ec5146cac692620efae2","tid":535330,"uid":140599,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:27:25.000Z","msg":"幫我含下撚會好d 架 信我"},{"pid":"b11ee958fbc55b741ac30bade9c371a528e62dfa","tid":535330,"uid":66772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:30:28.000Z","msg":"我有時同人呻好羨慕人地有個好溫馨既屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係成日聽返黎就係「再慘過你既都大把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},{"pid":"818671b8bb802a3bbf5b3702750a2ae3694ab0d1","tid":535330,"uid":165374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:36:13.000Z","msg":"咁又可以點(:"},{"pid":"6af142808a63e1b2eceb1f548e1b40220f8ec60f","tid":535330,"uid":62697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:40:08.000Z","msg":"Same here<br />\n老豆老母已經無講嘢接近半年<br />\n喺呢半年之前都係斷斷續續咁冷戰<br />\n最長個次應該有幾年<br />\n老豆曾經出軌<br />\n就算講返嘢個陣老母都間唔中會單單打打<br />\n自我有記憶以嚟一家人一齊出街嘅次數唔多過五次<br />\n因為老母掛住做嘢 連一齊旅行都未試過<br />\n好羨慕朋友屋企個個星期有一日family day 兩老仲好恩愛成日兩個出去拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178150707d71c33c1dc5b9c3016ae12e8a94d661","tid":535330,"uid":138800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:45:28.000Z","msg":"我屋企都係差唔多，不過父母喺我五歲時已經離咗婚。<br />\n<br />\n有時真係好羨慕人地一家人齊齊整整，好温馨好開心，喺街見到啲父母拖住個小朋友行街，我又會諗起自己細個一個人行無人拖，見到人地一家人一齊食飯，又會醒起自己已經13年無再試過一家人坐埋食餐飯。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢個屋企，我真係感覺唔到家，與其話係屋企，我覺得似係我喺度租住咗13年多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4da855de598895ed1d6d4c6725ee5f2a465d53","tid":535330,"uid":165202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:50:29.000Z","msg":"冇嗌交但好少交流 我印象中由細到大一家人出過街冇5次 一齊食過飯唔知有冇10次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3863f5471333b6f7e590c9f5431c7dade091df4","tid":535330,"uid":30647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T18:09:05.000Z","msg":"兩邊唔會講嘢, 一講嘢就鬧交, 問題不斷繼續, 永無休止<br />\n咁樣仲慘過單親家庭, 單親反而問題解決咗, <br />\n<br />\n夾係中間, 唔通開聲叫老豆老母離婚咩"},{"pid":"403ce821b1019f8d2715b5b474cda6a09d946c9e","tid":535330,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"我屋企都係咁<br />\n老豆老母分房瞓 呀媽北上返大陸走左成個月先返<br />\n兩公婆無計傾<br />\n我同家姐夾係中間好難受<br />\n好想離家出走<br />\n放棄依個咁既屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491d799f87613cda64eba714d82692b9655158c5","tid":535330,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T18:18:45.000Z","msg":"一樣..<br />\n小學離婚 阿媽改嫁 但老豆唔知<br />\n而家仲一直一齊住緊...<br />\n次次講親野都會嗌交<br />\n好羨慕人地屋企有家庭聚會果啲<br />\n因為我地屋企連普通交談都冇<br />\n我自已亦都睇化晒"},{"pid":"441dd20ee3a34bbf683a07785d2fe1233807b774","tid":535330,"uid":80447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6af142808a63e1b2eceb1f548e1b40220f8ec60f","tid":535330,"uid":62697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:40:08.000Z","msg":"Same here<br />\n老豆老母已經無講嘢接近半年<br />\n喺呢半年之前都係斷斷續續咁冷戰<br />\n最長個次應該有幾年<br />\n老豆曾經出軌<br />\n就算講返嘢個陣老母都間唔中會單單打打<br />\n自我有記憶以嚟一家人一齊出街嘅次數唔多過五次<br />\n因為老母掛住做嘢 連一齊旅行都未試過<br />\n好羨慕朋友屋企個個星期有一日family day 兩老仲好恩愛成日兩個出去拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T18:20:35.000Z","msg":"我屋企都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該準備離婚"}]}